creator: C. L. Freeston
description: LibriVox recording of Cycling in the Alps by C. L. Freeston. Read in English by Phil Benson. A guide to cycling in the European Alps in the days before surfaced roads and automobile tourism. As the author explains, the spectacular views are well worth the effort of pushing your bicycle up the passes and perfectly safe as long as your cycle is equipped with brakes. Summary by Phil Benson. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (106MB)
subject: librivox; audiobooks;bicycle; Switzerland; cycling; mountain; the alps; mountain biking; bike
title: Cycling in the Alps
